  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038580/extras/b6b15a103b696515d4426278155ca444.avif?t=1755114959\" width=1200 height=800 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Art Shop Simulator is a chill first-person game giving you the opportunity to unsleash your creativity. Join our community to get first hand news on updates and new features. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038580/extras/6a297378e70582b66e01efdcd40b0c53.webp?t=1755114959\" width=600 height=50 /></span>Dive into the world of art and express your creativity by crafting unique paintings. Use your imagination to create stunning artworks that will captivate your customers and give your shop the fame it deserves. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038580/extras/fc1c0207d06b7e5a714723a66af8c074.poster.avif?t=1755114959\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038580/extras/fc1c0207d06b7e5a714723a66af8c074.webm?t=1755114959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038580/extras/fc1c0207d06b7e5a714723a66af8c074.mp4?t=1755114959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038580/extras/7a06600e91250c05fb6941b4dec9fd02.webp?t=1755114959\" width=600 height=50 /></span>Take full control of your art shop's operations. Buy and place items, manage supplies, set prices, and optimize your shop's layout to maximize sales and customer satisfaction. Every decision counts in your journey to success.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038580/extras/5ebbf16a4d93ff53bcdca1b3dc849fb2.poster.avif?t=1755114959\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038580/extras/5ebbf16a4d93ff53bcdca1b3dc849fb2.webm?t=1755114959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038580/extras/5ebbf16a4d93ff53bcdca1b3dc849fb2.mp4?t=1755114959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038580/extras/f58d31cf87463c60e6e414758f5a99cc.webp?t=1755114959\" width=600 height=50 /></span>Watch your shop flourish as you gain recognition. Upgrade and expand your space to accommodate more customers and showcase a larger collection of art. Transform your humble beginnings into a renowned art gallery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038580/extras/65b4bfd38691fb39d56e5d87e4e65d14.poster.avif?t=1755114959\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038580/extras/65b4bfd38691fb39d56e5d87e4e65d14.webm?t=1755114959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038580/extras/65b4bfd38691fb39d56e5d87e4e65d14.mp4?t=1755114959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038580/extras/5b3f98820bc86777094fea3f78bb2e20.webp?t=1755114959\" width=600 height=50 /></span>Build a team to support your growing business. Hire skilled employees to handle daily operations and talented artists to produce high-quality paintings. Manage your staff effectively to ensure a smooth and thriving shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038580/extras/c2ada4884c65f3fff3a620dbb1c356c7.poster.avif?t=1755114959\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038580/extras/c2ada4884c65f3fff3a620dbb1c356c7.webm?t=1755114959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038580/extras/c2ada4884c65f3fff3a620dbb1c356c7.mp4?t=1755114959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038580/extras/2ab21478c455ad564c2340ab1a123562.webp?t=1755114959\" width=600 height=50 /></span>Challenge yourself to rise above the competition. Strategize, innovate, and outperform rival art shops to become the most prestigious art dealer in Europe. Your journey to the top is filled with exciting challenges and rewards.</p>",
